    <date day="08" month="May" year="2001"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines the LDAP Client Update Protocol (LCUP). The 
protocol is intended to allow an LDAP client to synchronize with the 
content of a directory information tree (DIT) stored by an LDAP 
server and to be notified about the changes to that content.</t>
    </abstract>
